*Plati*o je račun na vreme. (He paid the bill on time.)

*Plaća* se u banki. (It is paid in the bank.)

*Plaćen*o je svim potrebnim porezima. (It was paid with all the necessary taxes.)

*Plaćeno* je odmah. (It was paid immediately.)

*Plaćaju* se nadoknade za radnike. (Compensations are paid for the workers.)

*Plaćate* li kupljenu stvar? (Are you paying for the purchased item?)